examples.en: The baby has a dirty diaper.
I bathed him and changed his diaper.

examples.en: Make sure you put the baby's diaper on before you start feeding her. I learned this lesson the hard way.

examples.en: I put the dirty diaper in the trash.
examples.ru: Грязный подгузник я выбросил в мусорное ведро.
